      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) verification must be demonstrated for all governing equations used in the hemolysis model.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was performed only for the Navier-Stokes solver; the power-law hemolysis damage model was not independently verified. Achieved level 2 is below the required level 4."
    },
    {
