      "rationale": "Three-level grid convergence study was performed at two of five operating points; remaining three points used a single-level refinement check. GCI values at assessed points are acceptable but coverage is insufficient for MRL 5. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
