      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must cover the full VAD operating envelope (5 flow-speed combinations) with geometry identical or analytically traceable to the FDA generic pump geometry.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry at 3 of 5 required operating points. The two omitted points correspond to the highest-risk high-speed low-flow conditions most relevant to VAD use. Achieved level 2 is below required level 4."
    },
