      "acceptanceCriteria": "Evidence of independent review of model setup, boundary condition specification, and post-processing procedures must be provided to rule out operator-introduced errors.",
      "rationale": "No independent review of model setup was performed. A single analyst prepared and executed all simulations. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
