      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity analysis must demonstrate that uncertainty in blood rheological parameters (viscosity, yield stress, hematocrit) does not dominate total hemolysis prediction uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was performed on geometric and flow boundary condition parameters but blood rheological parameters were held fixed at nominal values. Sensitivity to rheological inputs was not assessed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
