      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples must be characterized for lot-to-lot variability in hemolytic susceptibility, and a minimum of three independent experimental replicates must be reported per operating point.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data were drawn from a single lot of bovine blood with no inter-lot variability characterization. Replicate count per operating point is not reported. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
