    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted as a complete record of the MRL 5 evaluation for the VAD hemolysis COU. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or formally flagged as epistemic gaps. The package is submitted for regulatory review with the understanding that six factors remain unassessed and that all assessed factors fall below required levels, resulting in an overall Not Accepted determination for model use. The UnitOfAssurance itself is accepted as a faithful representation of the assessment state. Note: the signing algorithm (ed25519) is declared but the signature value was not finalized prior to submission; structural integrity verification is pending.",
